Day 30 - 710*
Two small stories, the second worse than the first.
The first has some alarming mistakes, for example, the breasts look like ready to burst balloons and the white censorship prevents the reader from truly appreciating the work that was made.
The second part, has too the horrible white censorship but with the addition of a thin waist and overly big stature.
Overall, it really needs to be worked on before becoming something good.
1/10.
Also, I've been here for about an hour and still only did ten. I have a long way to go.
